name: Nod-Krai Hot Dog
desc: Classic convenience food. Put a sausage in some bread, sprinkle on some fried onions, a generous squirt of sauce... and there you go, a delicious, filling Nod-Krai Hot Dog!

value.text: Increases all party members' CRIT Rate by 9% for 300s. In Co-Op Mode, this effect only applies to your own character(s).
